    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for checking out my car! It's been such a reliable ride and I'm honestly a bit sad to see it go. It's in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-loved and well-maintained, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner right away. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. Everything runs smoothly, and it\u2019s just a great, dependable vehicle. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
