    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a mechanically sound example of the legendary E46 platform, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This unit is equipped with a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The double-VANOS system has been meticulously serviced to ensure a smooth power curve, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue. The suspension retains its sharp handling characteristics through refreshed bushings and high-rate dampers. While the exterior shows minor signs of use, the drivetrain and longitudinal balance remain exceptional, offering a pure analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
