    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a vehicle that perfectly balances luxury and reliability. This car has been a dedicated daily companion, maintained with an eye for detail. The exterior finish is vibrant, showing only the expected minor character marks from the open road, while the alloy wheels remain crisp and clean. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free interior where the upholstery has been preserved with regular conditioning, and every button and dial operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, a testament to a strict adherence to its service intervals. We recently performed a full fluid flush and a multi-point inspection to ensure it\u2019s ready for its next chapter. It drives straight, brakes firmly, and offers a level of comfort that makes every commute a pleasure. This is a complete package for a discerning buyer looking for a well-maintained, dependable ride.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
