    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs beautifully, and has been super well-loved. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready for its next adventure with you. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
