      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This example has been meticulously sorted with a reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings, addressing the chassis and internal vulnerabilities common to the platform. Power is channeled through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The suspension geometry remains precise, benefiting from refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with regular use, the powertrain synchronization and throttle response remain razor-sharp for the discerning enthusiast.",
